item.title: CVE-2022-1962|2024-08-03T00:24:43.737Z -- go%20standard%20library -- go%2Fparser
item.description: Uncontrolled recursion in the Parse functions in go/parser before Go 1.17.12 and Go 1.18.4 allow an attacker to cause a panic due to stack exhaustion via deeply nested types or declarations.
